OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after car hits
OL,4,Cfive pedestrians in west London
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after a car
OL,8,Fcollided with multiple pedestrians in
OL,9,Fwest London before driving away,
OL,10,Fpolice have said.
OL,12,FFive people were injured in the
OL,13,Fincident in Ealing on Saturday
OL,14,Fafternoon, although none have suffered
OL,15,Flife-threatening or life-changing
OL,16,Finjuries.
OL,18,FCounter Terrorism Policing (CTP)
OL,19,FLondon conducted initial inquiries,
OL,20,Fbut it is not being treated as
OL,21,Fterrorism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
