OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782634701
OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after car hits
OL,4,Cfive pedestrians in west London
OL,6,FThe Somalia-born British driver was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving and attempted murder, the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,11,FHe did not wait at the scene but was
OL,12,Fstopped in nearby Grange Park "a short
OL,13,Ftime later", the force added.
OL,15,FThree of those injured were taken to
OL,16,Fhospital, while two others were
OL,17,Ftreated at the scene.
