OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after car hits
OL,4,Cfive pedestrians in west London
OL,6,FA force spokesperson said: "Due to the
OL,7,Fnature of the incident, local officers
OL,8,Fwere in contact with officers from
OL,9,FCounter Terrorism Policing London as
OL,10,Fthey conducted their initial
OL,11,Fenquiries. While investigators are
OL,12,Fkeeping an open mind as to any
OL,13,Fpotential motive, the incident is not
OL,14,Fbeing treated as terrorism."
