OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after car hits
OL,4,Cfive pedestrians in west London
OL,6,FA London Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fspokesperson said it was called to
OL,8,Freports of a road traffic collision at
OL,9,F2.29pm.
OL,11,FThey said: "We sent a number of
OL,12,Fresources including ambulance crews,
OL,13,Fparamedics in fast response cars, a
OL,14,Fvolunteer emergency responder crew and
OL,15,Fan incident response officer to the
OL,16,Fscene. We also dispatched London's Air
OL,17,FAmbulance.
