OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after car hits
OL,4,Cfive pedestrians in west London
OL,6,F"We treated three patients at the
OL,7,Fscene and took one of them to a major
OL,8,Ftrauma centre by road as a priority.
OL,9,FThe other two patients were taken to a
OL,10,Flocal hospital."
